reviewText: DVD is incomplete!!!! Not full movie.....what the hell??!! Don't buy!!
This DVD stops after 45 minutes! Others who have purchased this movie have the same problem!

The first copy I bought of this only had 46 minutes on it. Amazon were great and sent me a second copy - It only had 47.5 minutes on it. So I can't do a review on it as I haven't seen it all yet.  Very disappointing.
